# Build
# NOTE: dist/ is intentionally committed on this deploy branch — Render's free build
# tier lacks the RAM to run `tsc` over the @larksuiteoapi/node-sdk type surface (tsc OOMs).
# We ship the prebuilt output and Render only installs runtime deps. Rebuild with `yarn build`.
